<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb n="0001a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><head type="no">No. 1957</head>
<lb n="0001a02"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="0001001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】德川時代刊宗教大學藏本，【甲】延寶五年刊大谷大學藏本，【敦】唐景雲二年寫佛蘭西國民圖書館藏燉煌本</note>略論安樂淨土義</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0001a03"/>
<lb n="0001a04"/><byline type="Author"><note n="0001002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原本註曰釋曇鸞撰一作曇鸞法師作，愚案此皆後人所安蓋原文無撰者之號然欲顯別故今且從一本標之，〔釋曇鸞撰〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001002"><lem>釋曇鸞撰</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0001002" place="foot" type="rest">原本註曰釋曇鸞撰一作曇鸞法師作，愚案此皆後人所安蓋原文無撰者之號然欲顯別故今且從一本標之</note></byline>
<lb n="0001a05"/><div1 type="jing"><p>問曰。安樂國於三界中何界所攝</p>
<lb n="0001a06"/><p>答曰。<note n="0001003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001003"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>釋論言。如斯淨土非三界所攝。何
<lb n="0001a07"/>以故。無欲故非欲界。地居故非色界。有<note n="0001004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔形〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001004"><lem>形</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0001a08"/>色故非無色界。經曰。<note n="0001005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001005"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>彌陀佛本行菩薩道
<lb n="0001a09"/>時。作比丘。名曰法藏。於世自在王佛所。<note n="0001006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔請〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001006"><lem>請</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0001a10"/>問諸佛淨土之行。時佛為說二百一十億諸
<lb n="0001a11"/>佛剎土天人善惡國土精&CB00308;。悉現與之。于時
<lb n="0001a12"/>法藏菩薩。即於佛前。發弘誓大願。取諸佛土。
<lb n="0001a13"/>於無量阿僧祇劫。如所發願。行諸波羅蜜。萬
<lb n="0001a14"/>善圓滿。成無上道。別業所得。非三界也</p>
<lb n="0001a15"/><p>問曰。安樂國有幾種莊嚴。名為淨土</p>
<lb n="0001a16"/><p>答曰。若依經據義。法藏菩薩四十八願即是
<lb n="0001a17"/><note n="0001007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001007"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>事。尋讚可知。不復重序。若依無量壽論。
<lb n="0001a18"/>以二種清淨。攝二十九種莊嚴成就。二種清
<lb n="0001a19"/>淨者。一器世間<note n="0001008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔清淨〕－【甲】</note><app n="0001008"><lem>清淨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。二是眾生世間清淨。
<lb n="0001a20"/>器世間清淨有十七種莊嚴成就。一者。國土
<lb n="0001a21"/>相勝過三界道。二者。其國廣大。量如虛空。無
<lb n="0001a22"/>有齊限。三者。從菩薩正道大慈悲出世善根
<lb n="0001a23"/>所起。四者。清淨光明圓滿莊嚴。五者。備具第
<lb n="0001a24"/>一珍寶性。出奇妙寶物。六者<note n="0001009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">潔＋（清）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0001009"><lem>潔</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">潔清</rdg></app>淨光明常照
<lb n="0001a25"/>世間。七者。其國寶物柔軟。觸者適悅。生於勝
<lb n="0001a26"/>樂。八者。千萬寶華莊嚴池沼。寶殿寶樓閣種
<lb n="0001a27"/>種寶樹雜色光明影<note n="0001010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">納＝細&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0001010"><lem>納</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">細</rdg></app>世界。無量寶<note n="0001011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">網＋（羅）【敦】</note><app n="0001011"><lem>網</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">網羅</rdg></app>覆
<lb n="0001a28"/>虛空。四面懸鈴常吐法音。九者。於虛空中。自
<lb n="0001a29"/>然常雨天華<note n="0001012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔天〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001012"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>衣天香。莊嚴普熏。十者。佛
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0001b" n="0001b"/>
<lb n="0001b01"/>慧光明照除癡闇。十一者。梵聲開悟遠聞十
<lb n="0001b02"/>方。十二者。阿彌陀佛無上法王善力住持。十
<lb n="0001b03"/>三者。從如來淨華所化生。十四者。愛樂佛法
<lb n="0001b04"/>味。禪三昧為食。十五者。永離身心諸苦。受樂
<lb n="0001b05"/>無間。十六者。乃至不聞二乘女人根缺之名。
<lb n="0001b06"/>十七者。眾生有所欲樂。隨心稱意。無不滿足。
<lb n="0001b07"/>如是等<note n="0001013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十七種〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001013"><lem>十七種</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。是名器世間清淨。眾生世間
<lb n="0001b08"/>清淨有十二種莊嚴成就。一者。無量大珍寶
<lb n="0001b09"/><note n="0001014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001014"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>微妙華臺以為佛座。二者。無量相好無量
<lb n="0001b10"/>光明莊嚴佛身。三者。佛無量<app><lem>辯</lem><rdg wit="【大】">辨</rdg></app>才應機說法。
<lb n="0001b11"/>具足清白。令人樂聞。聞者必悟解。言不虛
<lb n="0001b12"/><note n="0001015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＝設【敦】</note><app n="0001015"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">設</rdg></app>。四者。佛真如智慧猶如虛空。照了諸法
<lb n="0001b13"/>總相別相。心無分別。五者。天人不動眾廣大
<lb n="0001b14"/>莊嚴。<note n="0001016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原本註曰譬如等十五字當移次下況復過者下</note>譬如須彌山映顯四大海。法王相具足。
<lb n="0001b15"/>六者。成就無上果。尚無能及。況復過者。<note n="0001017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七者〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001017"><lem>七
<lb n="0001b16"/>者</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。為天人丈夫調御師。大眾恭敬圍遶。如師
<lb n="0001b17"/>子王師子<note n="0001018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔圍〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001018"><lem>圍</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>遶。八者。佛本願力莊嚴住持諸
<lb n="0001b18"/>功德。遇者無空過。能令速滿足一切功德海。
<lb n="0001b19"/><note n="0001019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（與）&M062403;＋未【原】，未證＝與諸【敦】</note><note n="0001019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未證＝與諸【敦】，（與）&M062403;＋未【原】</note><app n="0001019"><lem>未證</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">與諸</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">與未證</rdg></app>淨心菩薩畢竟得<note n="0001020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔證〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001020"><lem>證</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>平等法身。與淨
<lb n="0001b20"/>心菩薩與上地菩薩。畢竟同得寂滅平等。九
<lb n="0001b21"/>者。安樂國諸菩薩眾。身不動搖而遍至十方。
<lb n="0001b22"/>種種應化。如實修行。常作佛事。十者。如是菩
<lb n="0001b23"/>薩應化身。一切時不前不後。一心一念放<note n="0001021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001021"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0001b24"/>光明。悉能遍至十方世界。教化眾生。種種方
<lb n="0001b25"/>便。修行所成。滅除一切眾生苦惱。十一者。是
<lb n="0001b26"/>等菩薩於一切世界無餘照諸佛大會。無餘
<lb n="0001b27"/>廣大無量供養恭敬讚歎諸佛如來功德。十
<lb n="0001b28"/>二者。是諸菩薩於十方一切世界無三寶處。
<lb n="0001b29"/>住持莊嚴佛法僧<note n="0001022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寶〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001022"><lem>寶</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>功德大海。遍示令解。如
<lb n="0001b30"/>實修行。如是等法王八種莊嚴功德成就。如
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0001c" n="0001c"/>
<lb n="0001c01"/>是菩薩四種莊嚴功德成就。是名眾生世間
<lb n="0001c02"/>清淨。安樂國土具如是等二十九種莊嚴功
<lb n="0001c03"/>德成就。故名淨土</p>
<lb n="0001c04"/><p>問曰。生安樂土者。凡有幾<note n="0001023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔品〕&M062403;－【原】，品輩有幾＝輩輩有【敦】</note><note n="0001023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">品輩有幾＝輩輩有【敦】，〔品〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001023"><lem>品輩。有幾</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">輩輩有</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">輩有幾</rdg></app>因緣</p>
<lb n="0001c05"/><p>答曰。無量壽經中。唯有三輩上中下。無量壽
<lb n="0001c06"/>觀經中。一<note n="0001024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">品＋（中）【敦】</note><app n="0001024"><lem>品</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">品中</rdg></app>又分為上中下。三三而九。合
<lb n="0001c07"/>為九品。<note n="0001025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＝令&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0001025"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">令</rdg></app>依傍無量壽經為讚。且據此經
<lb n="0001c08"/><note n="0001026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001026"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三品論之。上輩生者有五因緣。一者。捨
<lb n="0001c09"/>家離欲而作沙門。二者。發無上菩提<note n="0001027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0001027"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。三
<lb n="0001c10"/>者。一向專念無量壽佛。四者。修諸功德。五
<lb n="0001c11"/>者。願生安樂國。具此<note n="0001028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔因〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001028"><lem>因</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>緣。臨命終時。無量
<lb n="0001c12"/>壽佛與諸大眾現其人前。即便隨佛。往生安
<lb n="0001c13"/>樂。於七寶華中。自然化生。住不退轉。智慧勇
<lb n="0001c14"/>猛。神通自在。中輩生者有七因緣。一者。發無
<lb n="0001c15"/>上菩提心。二者。一向專念無量壽佛。三者。<note n="0001029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多少＝少多【敦】</note><app n="0001029"><lem>多
<lb n="0001c16"/>少</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">少多</rdg></app>修善奉持齋戒。四者。起立塔像。五者。<note n="0001030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝飲&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0001030"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">飲</rdg></app>
<lb n="0001c17"/>食沙門。六者。懸繒<note n="0001031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">然＝燃【敦】</note><app n="0001031"><lem>然</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">燃</rdg></app>燈。散華燒香。七者。以
<lb n="0001c18"/>此迴向願生安樂。臨命終時。無量壽佛化現
<lb n="0001c19"/>其身。光明相好具如真佛。與諸大眾現其人
<lb n="0001c20"/>前。即隨化佛往生安<note n="0001032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樂＋（國）【甲】</note><app n="0001032"><lem>樂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">樂國</rdg></app>。住不退轉。功德智
<lb n="0001c21"/>慧次<note n="0001033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001033"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>上輩<note n="0001034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（下輩…中輩）七十二字∞（又有…安樂）七十字【敦】</note><note n="0001034" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>（下輩…中輩）七十二字∞（又有…安樂）七十字【敦】</note>下輩生者有三因緣。一者。假使
<lb n="0001c22"/>不能作諸功德。當發無上菩提心。二者。一向
<lb n="0001c23"/>專意乃至十念念無量壽佛。三者。以至誠心
<lb n="0001c24"/>願生安樂。臨命終時。夢見無量壽佛。亦得往
<lb n="0001c25"/>生。功德智慧次如中輩。<note n="0001035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（下輩…中輩）七十二字∞（又有…安樂）七十字【敦】</note><note n="0001035" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>（下輩…中輩）七十二字∞（又有…安樂）七十字【敦】</note>又有一種往生安樂
<lb n="0001c26"/>不入三輩中。謂以疑惑心。修<note n="0001036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【敦】</note><app n="0001036"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>功德。願生
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb n="0002a01"/>安樂。不了佛智不思議智不可稱智大乘廣
<lb n="0002a02"/>智無等無倫最上勝智。於此諸智疑惑不信。
<lb n="0002a03"/>然猶信罪福修習善本。<note n="0002001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生安樂〕－&M062485;【原】，生安樂＝願生【敦】</note><app n="0002001"><lem><sic corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">生安樂</sic></lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">願生</rdg></app><note n="0002002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（又有一種往生安樂不入三輩中謂以疑惑心修諸功德不異前說）＋生【敦】</note><app n="0002002"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">又有一種往生安樂不入三輩中謂以疑惑心修諸功德不異前說生</rdg></app>安樂國
<lb n="0002a04"/><note n="0002003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝已十【敦】</note><app n="0002003"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">已十</rdg></app>寶宮殿。或百由旬惑五百由旬。各於其中
<lb n="0002a05"/>受諸快樂。如忉利天。亦皆自然。於五百歲中。
<lb n="0002a06"/><note n="0002004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔常〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002004"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不見佛。不聞經法。不見菩薩聲聞聖眾。
<lb n="0002a07"/>安樂國土謂之邊地。亦曰胎生。邊地者。言其
<lb n="0002a08"/>五百歲中不見聞三寶。義同邊地之難。或亦
<lb n="0002a09"/>於安樂國土最在其邊。胎生者。譬如胎生人
<lb n="0002a10"/>初生之時人法未成。邊言其難。胎言其闇。此
<lb n="0002a11"/>二名皆借此況彼耳。非是八難中邊地。亦非
<lb n="0002a12"/>胞胎中胎生。何以知之。安樂國<note n="0002005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔土〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002005"><lem>土</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一<note n="0002006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔向〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0002006"><lem>向</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>化
<lb n="0002a13"/>生故。故知非實胎生。五百年後還得見聞三
<lb n="0002a14"/>寶故。故知非八難中邊地也</p>
<lb n="0002a15"/><p>問曰。彼胎生者處七寶宮殿中受快樂<note n="0002007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔否〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002007"><lem>否</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。復
<lb n="0002a16"/>何所憶念</p>
<lb n="0002a17"/><p>答曰。經喻云。譬如轉輪王子得罪於王。內
<lb n="0002a18"/><note n="0002008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝著【敦】</note><app n="0002008"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>後宮。繫以金鎖。一切供<note n="0002009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝見【敦】</note><app n="0002009"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">見</rdg></app>無所乏少。猶
<lb n="0002a19"/>如<note n="0002010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＋（子）【敦】</note><app n="0002010"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">王子</rdg></app>。王子于時雖有好妙種種自娛樂<note n="0002011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝其【敦】</note><app n="0002011"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">其</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0002a20"/>心不<note n="0002012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝愛【敦】</note><app n="0002012"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">愛</rdg></app>樂。但<note n="0002013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔念〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0002013" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">念</sic>設<note n="0002014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002014"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>方便求免悕出。彼胎
<lb n="0002a21"/>生者亦復如是。雖處七寶宮殿有<note n="0002015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好色＝妙色聲【敦】</note><app n="0002015"><lem>好色</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">妙色聲</rdg></app>香味
<lb n="0002a22"/>觸。不以為樂。但<note n="0002016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝以&M062403;【原】，（以）＋不【敦】</note><app n="0002016"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">以</rdg><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">以不</rdg></app>見三寶。不得供養修諸
<lb n="0002a23"/>善本。以之為苦。識其本罪。深自<note n="0002017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">責悔＝悔責【敦】</note><app n="0002017"><lem>責悔</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">悔責</rdg></app>。求離
<lb n="0002a24"/>彼處。即得如意。還同三輩生者。當是五百年
<lb n="0002a25"/>末方識罪<note n="0002018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（生）＋悔【敦】</note><app n="0002018"><lem>悔</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">生悔</rdg></app>耳</p>
<lb n="0002a26"/><p>問曰。以疑惑心往生安樂名曰胎生者。云何
<lb n="0002a27"/>起疑</p>
<lb n="0002a28"/><p>答曰。經中但云疑惑不信。不出所以疑意。尋
<lb n="0002a29"/>不了五句。敢以對治言之。不了佛智者。謂不
<lb n="0002a30"/>能信了佛一切種智。不了故<note n="0002019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002019"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>起疑。此一句
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0002b" n="0002b"/>
<lb n="0002b01"/>總辨所疑。下四句一一對治所疑。疑有四意。
<lb n="0002b02"/>一者疑。<note n="0002020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔但〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002020"><lem>但</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>憶念阿彌陀佛。不必得往生安
<lb n="0002b03"/>樂。何以故。經言。業道如<note n="0002021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">秤＝科【敦】</note><app n="0002021"><lem>秤</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">科</rdg></app>。重者先牽。云何
<lb n="0002b04"/>一生或百年。或十年<note n="0002022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或一月＝一日【敦】</note><app n="0002022"><lem>或一月</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">一日</rdg></app>。無惡不造。但
<lb n="0002b05"/>以十念相續便得往生。即入正定聚。畢竟不
<lb n="0002b06"/>退。與三途諸苦永隔<note n="0002023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝耶【敦】＊</note><app n="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>。若爾。先牽之義何
<lb n="0002b07"/>以<note n="0002024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝取【敦】</note><app n="0002024"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>信。又曠劫已來<note n="0002025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俱＝備【敦】</note><app n="0002025"><lem>俱</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">備</rdg></app>造諸行有漏之法
<lb n="0002b08"/>繫屬三界。云何不斷三界結惑。直以少時念
<lb n="0002b09"/>阿彌陀佛。便出三界<app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。繫業之義復欲云何。
<lb n="0002b10"/>對治此疑故言不思議智。不思議智者。謂佛
<lb n="0002b11"/>智力能以少作多。<note n="0002026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以多〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002026"><lem>以多</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作少。以近為遠。以
<lb n="0002b12"/>遠為近。以輕為重。以重為輕。以長為短。以短
<lb n="0002b13"/>為長。如是等<note n="0002027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002027"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>智無量無邊不可思議。譬如
<lb n="0002b14"/>百夫百年聚薪積高千仞。豆許火焚。半日便
<lb n="0002b15"/>盡。<note n="0002028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔豈…盡〕十三字－【敦】</note><app n="0002028" word-count="13"><lem>豈可得言百年之薪積半日不盡</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。又
<lb n="0002b16"/>如躄者寄載他船。因風帆勢。一日至千里。豈
<lb n="0002b17"/>可得言躄者云何一日至千里<app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。又如下賤貧
<lb n="0002b18"/>人獲一瑞物而以貢<note n="0002029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝王【敦】＊</note><note n="0002029" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>主＝王【敦】＊</note><app n="0002029"><lem>主</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>。主慶所得加諸重賞。
<lb n="0002b19"/>斯須之頃富貴盈<note n="0002030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">溢＝望【敦】</note><app n="0002030"><lem>溢</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">望</rdg></app>。豈可得<note n="0002031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言以可有＝以【敦】</note><app n="0002031"><lem>言以可有</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>數十
<lb n="0002b20"/>年<note n="0002032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（貧）＋仕【敦】</note><app n="0002032"><lem>仕</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">貧仕</rdg></app>備盡辛懃。<note n="0002033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上下尚〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002033"><lem>上下尚</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不達歸者。<note n="0002034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝謂&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0002034" corr="謂" resp="【原】">言</sic>彼富
<lb n="0002b21"/>貴無此事<app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。又如劣夫以己身力擲驢不上。
<lb n="0002b22"/>從轉輪王行。便乘虛空飛騰自<note n="0002035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">然＝在【敦】</note><app n="0002035"><lem>然</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">在</rdg></app>。復<note n="0002036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">可＋（得）【敦】</note><app n="0002036"><lem>可</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">可得</rdg></app>以
<lb n="0002b23"/>擲驢之劣<note n="0002037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔夫〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002037"><lem>夫</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。言必不能乘空耶。又如十圍之
<lb n="0002b24"/>索千夫不制。童子揮劍瞬頃兩分。豈可得言
<lb n="0002b25"/>一小兒力不<note n="0002038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔能〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002038"><lem>能</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>斷索<app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。又如鴆鳥入水魚&CB01108;
<lb n="0002b26"/>斯斃。犀角觸泥死者咸起。豈可得言性命一
<lb n="0002b27"/>斷無可生<app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。又如黃鵠呼子安。<note n="0002039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔子安〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002039"><lem>子安</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>還活。
<lb n="0002b28"/>豈可得言墳下千歲<note n="0002040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔齡〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002040"><lem>齡</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>決無可甦<app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。一切萬
<lb n="0002b29"/>法皆有自力他力自攝他攝。千開萬<note n="0002041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">閉＝開&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0002041"><lem>閉</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">開</rdg></app>無量
<lb n="0002b30"/>無邊。安得以有礙之識疑<note n="0002042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔彼〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002042"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無礙之法乎。又
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0002c" n="0002c"/>
<lb n="0002c01"/>五不思議中。佛法最不可思議。而以百年之
<lb n="0002c02"/>惡為重。疑十念念佛為輕。不得往生安樂入
<lb n="0002c03"/>正定聚者。是事不然。二者疑。佛智於人不為
<lb n="0002c04"/>玄絕。何以故。夫一切名字從相待生。覺智從
<lb n="0002c05"/>不覺生。如<note n="0002043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002043"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>迷方從記方生。若便迷絕不
<lb n="0002c06"/>迷。迷卒不解。迷若可解。必迷者解。亦可云解
<lb n="0002c07"/>者<note n="0002044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迷＋（解）【敦】</note><app n="0002044"><lem>迷</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">迷解</rdg></app>。迷解解迷猶手反覆耳。乃可明昧為
<lb n="0002c08"/>異。亦安得超然哉。起此疑故。於佛智慧生疑
<lb n="0002c09"/>不信。對治此疑故言不可稱智。不可稱智者。
<lb n="0002c10"/>言佛智絕稱謂。非相形待。何以言之。法若是
<lb n="0002c11"/>有。必<note n="0002045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔應〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002045"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>有知有之智。法若是無。亦應有知
<lb n="0002c12"/>無之<note n="0002046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＋（法若是無亦應有知無之智）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0002046"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">智法若是無亦應有知無之智</rdg></app>。諸法離於有無。故佛冥諸法。則智
<lb n="0002c13"/>絕相待。汝引解迷為喻。猶是一迷耳。不成迷
<lb n="0002c14"/>解。亦如夢中與他解夢。雖云解夢。非是不夢。
<lb n="0002c15"/>以知取佛。不曰知佛。以不知取佛。<note n="0002047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（亦）＋非【敦】</note><app n="0002047"><lem>非</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">亦非</rdg></app>知佛。
<lb n="0002c16"/>以非知非不知取佛。亦非知佛。以非非<note n="0002048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知＝智&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0002048"><lem>知</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">智</rdg></app>非
<lb n="0002c17"/>非不知取佛。亦非知佛。佛智離此四句。緣之
<lb n="0002c18"/>者心行滅。<note n="0002049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">損＝指【敦】</note><app n="0002049"><lem>損</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">指</rdg></app>之者言語斷。以是義故。釋論
<lb n="0002c19"/>云。若人<note n="0002050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＋（眾）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0002050"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">見眾</rdg></app>般若。是則為被縛。若不見般若。
<lb n="0002c20"/>是亦為被縛。若人見般若。是則為解脫。若不
<lb n="0002c21"/>見般若。是亦為解脫。此偈中說。不離四句者
<lb n="0002c22"/>為縛。離四句者為<note n="0002051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔解〕－【敦】</note><app n="0002051"><lem>解</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>脫。汝疑佛智與人不玄
<lb n="0002c23"/>絕者。是事不然。三者疑。佛<note n="0002052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">實不能＝不能實【甲】【敦】＊</note><app n="0002052"><lem>實不能</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【敦】" resp="Taisho">不能實</rdg></app>度一切
<lb n="0002c24"/>眾生。何以故。過去世有無量阿僧祇&M010527;沙諸
<lb n="0002c25"/>佛。現在十方世界亦有無量無邊阿僧祇&M010527;
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb n="0003a01"/>沙諸佛。若<note n="0003001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">使＝便【甲】</note><app n="0003001"><lem>使</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">便</rdg></app>佛實能度一切眾生。則應久無
<lb n="0003a02"/><note n="0003002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（復）＋三【敦】</note><app n="0003002"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">復三</rdg></app>界。第二佛則不應復為眾生發菩提心。具
<lb n="0003a03"/>修淨土攝受眾生。而實有第二佛。攝受眾生。
<lb n="0003a04"/>乃至實有三世十方無量諸佛。攝受眾生。故
<lb n="0003a05"/>知。佛實不能度一切眾生。起此疑故。於阿彌
<lb n="0003a06"/>陀佛作有量想。對治此疑故言大乘廣智。大
<lb n="0003a07"/>乘廣智者。言<note n="0003003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0003003"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無法不知。無煩惱不斷。無
<lb n="0003a08"/>善不備。無眾生不度。所以有三世十<note n="0003004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方＋（佛）【敦】</note><app n="0003004"><lem>方</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">方佛</rdg></app>者。
<lb n="0003a09"/>有五義。一者。若<note n="0003005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使【敦】＊</note><app n="0003005"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>無第二佛。乃至無阿僧
<lb n="0003a10"/>祇&M010527;沙諸佛者。佛便不能度一切眾生。以實
<lb n="0003a11"/>能度一切眾<note n="0003006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生〕－【敦】</note><app n="0003006"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>故。則有十方無量諸佛。<note n="0003007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無量〕－【敦】</note><app n="0003007"><lem>無
<lb n="0003a12"/>量</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>諸佛即是前佛所度眾生。二者。若一佛度
<lb n="0003a13"/>一切眾生盡者。<note n="0003008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝後【敦】</note><app n="0003008"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">後</rdg></app>亦不應<note n="0003009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後＝復【敦】</note><app n="0003009"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>有佛。何以故。
<lb n="0003a14"/>無覺他義故。復依何義。說有三世佛<note n="0003010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝取【敦】</note><app n="0003010"><lem>乎</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>。依
<lb n="0003a15"/>覺他義故。說佛佛皆度一切眾生。三者。後佛
<lb n="0003a16"/>能度。猶是前佛之能。何以故。由前佛有後佛
<lb n="0003a17"/>故。譬如帝王之<note n="0003011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲＝胄【敦】</note><app n="0003011"><lem>甲</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">胄</rdg></app>得相紹襲後<note n="0003012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【甲】</note><app n="0003012"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>。即是前
<lb n="0003a18"/>王之能故。四者。佛力雖能度<note n="0003013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一切〕－【敦】</note><app n="0003013"><lem>一切</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>眾生。要須
<lb n="0003a19"/>有因緣。若眾生與前佛無因緣。復須後佛。如
<lb n="0003a20"/>是無緣眾生動逕百千萬佛。不聞不見。非佛
<lb n="0003a21"/>力劣也。譬如日月周四天下破諸闇<note n="0003014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冥＝&CB13754;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0003014"><lem>冥</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&CB13754;</rdg></app>。而盲
<lb n="0003a22"/>者不見。非日不明也。雷<note n="0003015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">震裂＝聲震【敦】</note><app n="0003015"><lem>震裂</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">聲震</rdg></app>耳。而聾者不
<lb n="0003a23"/>聞。非聲不勵也。覺諸緣理。號之曰佛。若情強
<lb n="0003a24"/>違緣<note n="0003016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔理〕－【敦】</note><app n="0003016"><lem>理</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。非正覺也。是故眾生無量。佛亦無
<lb n="0003a25"/>量。<note n="0003017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徵＝微&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0003017"><lem>徵</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">微</rdg></app>佛莫問有緣無緣。何不盡度一切眾生
<lb n="0003a26"/>者。非理言也。<note n="0003018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五＋（者）【敦】</note><app n="0003018"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">五者</rdg></app>。眾生若盡。世間<note n="0003019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即墮＝則隨&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0003019"><lem>即墮</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">則隨</rdg></app>有邊。
<lb n="0003a27"/>以是義故則有無量佛。度一切眾生。問曰。若
<lb n="0003a28"/>眾生不可盡。世間復須墮無邊。無邊故佛則
<lb n="0003a29"/><app type="＊" source="0002052"><lem>實不能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【敦】">不能實</rdg></app>度一切眾生。答曰。世間非有邊非無
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0003b" n="0003b"/>
<lb n="0003b01"/>邊。亦絕四句。佛令眾生離此四句。名之為度。
<lb n="0003b02"/>其實非度非不度。非盡非不盡。譬如夢渡大
<lb n="0003b03"/>海。值濤波諸難。其人畏怖叫聲徹外。外人喚
<lb n="0003b04"/>覺。坦然無憂。但為渡夢。不為渡河。問曰。言
<lb n="0003b05"/>渡與不渡皆墮邊見。何以但說渡一切眾生
<lb n="0003b06"/>為大乘廣智。不說不渡眾生為大乘廣<note n="0003020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＋（耶）【敦】</note><app n="0003020"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">智耶</rdg></app>。答
<lb n="0003b07"/>曰。眾生莫不厭苦求樂畏縛求解。聞渡則歸
<lb n="0003b08"/>向。聞不渡不知所以不渡。便謂佛非大慈悲。
<lb n="0003b09"/>則不歸向。<note n="0003021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不歸向〕－【甲】</note><app n="0003021"><lem>不歸向</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>故長寢久夢。無由可息。
<lb n="0003b10"/>為是人故。多說渡不說不渡。復次<note n="0003022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸法〕－【敦】</note><app n="0003022"><lem>諸法</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無行
<lb n="0003b11"/>經亦言。佛不得佛道。亦不<note n="0003023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渡＝度【敦】＊</note><app n="0003023"><lem>渡</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">度</rdg></app>眾生。凡夫強
<lb n="0003b12"/>分別作佛。<app type="＊" source="0003023"><lem>渡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">度</rdg></app>眾生。言度眾生。是對治悉檀。
<lb n="0003b13"/>言不度眾生。是第一義悉檀。二言各有所以。
<lb n="0003b14"/>不相違背。問曰。如夢得息。豈不是度耶。若一
<lb n="0003b15"/>切眾生所夢皆息。世間豈不盡<app type="＊" source="0002023"><lem>乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">耶</rdg></app>。答曰。說
<lb n="0003b16"/>夢為世間。若夢息則無夢者。若無夢者亦不
<lb n="0003b17"/>說<note n="0003024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">度＝渡【敦】</note><app n="0003024"><lem>度</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">渡</rdg></app>者。如是知世間即<note n="0003025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝名【敦】</note><app n="0003025"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">名</rdg></app>出世間。雖度無
<lb n="0003b18"/>量眾生。則不墮顛倒。四者疑。佛不得一切種
<lb n="0003b19"/>智。何以故。<note n="0003026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（不）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0003026"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">若不</rdg></app>能遍知諸法。諸法墮有邊故。
<lb n="0003b20"/>若不能遍知。則非一切種智故。對治此疑故。
<lb n="0003b21"/>言無等無倫最上勝智。無等無倫最上勝智
<lb n="0003b22"/>者。凡夫智虛妄。佛智如實。虛實玄殊。理無得
<lb n="0003b23"/>等。故言無等。聲聞辟支佛欲有所知。入定方
<lb n="0003b24"/>知。出定不知。又知亦有限。佛得如實三昧。常
<lb n="0003b25"/>在深定。而遍知<note n="0003027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔照〕－【敦】</note><app n="0003027"><lem>照</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>萬法二與無二。深法非倫。
<lb n="0003b26"/>故言無倫。八地已上菩薩雖得報生三昧用無
<lb n="0003b27"/>出入。而習氣微熏三昧不極明淨。形待佛智。
<lb n="0003b28"/>猶為有上。佛智斷具足。如法而照。法無量故。
<lb n="0003b29"/>照亦無量。譬如函大蓋亦大。故<note n="0003028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言最上〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0003028"><lem>言最上</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>。此
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0003c" n="0003c"/>
<lb n="0003c01"/>三句亦可展轉相成。以佛智無與等者故。所
<lb n="0003c02"/>以無倫。以無倫故最上勝。亦可最上勝故無
<lb n="0003c03"/>等。無等故無倫。但言無等便足。復何以須下
<lb n="0003c04"/>二句者。如須陀洹智。不與阿羅漢等。而是其
<lb n="0003c05"/>類。初地至十地亦如是。智雖不等。非不其倫。
<lb n="0003c06"/>何以故。非最上故。汝以知有<note n="0003029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">邊＋（無邊）【敦】</note><app n="0003029"><lem>邊</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">邊無邊</rdg></app>為難。疑佛
<lb n="0003c07"/>非一切智者。是事不然</p>
<lb n="0003c08"/><p>問曰。下輩生中。云十念相續便得往生。云何
<lb n="0003c09"/>名為十念相續</p>
<lb n="0003c10"/><p>答<note n="0003030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【甲】</note><app n="0003030"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。譬如有人。空曠迴處值<note n="0003031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇＝愚&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0003031"><lem>遇</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">愚</rdg></app>怨賊。拔刃
<lb n="0003c11"/>奮勇。直<note n="0003032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔來〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0003032"><lem>來</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>欲<note n="0003033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殺＝取【敦】</note><app n="0003033"><lem>殺</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>。其人<note n="0003034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勁＝到【敦】</note><app n="0003034"><lem>勁</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">到</rdg></app>走<note n="0003035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">視＝頑【敦】</note><app n="0003035"><lem>視</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">頑</rdg></app>渡一河。若
<lb n="0003c12"/>得渡河。首領可全。爾時<note n="0003036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔但〕－【敦】</note><app n="0003036"><lem>但</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>念渡河方便。我
<lb n="0003c13"/>至河岸。為著衣渡。為脫衣渡。若著衣納。恐不
<lb n="0003c14"/>得過。若脫衣納。恐無得暇。但有此念更無他
<lb n="0003c15"/>緣。一念何當渡河。即是一念。如<note n="0003037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＋（十念）【敦】</note><app n="0003037"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">是十念</rdg></app>不雜<note n="0003038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（餘）＋心【敦】</note><app n="0003038"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">餘心</rdg></app>
<lb n="0003c16"/>名為十念相續。行者亦爾。念阿彌陀佛。如彼
<lb n="0003c17"/>念渡。逕于十念。若念佛名字。<note n="0003039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0003039"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>念佛相好。
<lb n="0003c18"/>若念佛光明。若念佛神力。若念佛功德。若念
<lb n="0003c19"/>佛智慧。若念佛本願。無他心間雜。心心相次
<lb n="0003c20"/>乃至十念。名為十念相續。一往言十念相續。
<lb n="0003c21"/>似若不難。然凡夫心猶野馬。識劇<note n="0003040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猿＝&CB00338;【敦】</note><app n="0003040"><lem>猿</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&CB00338;</rdg></app>猴。馳
<lb n="0003c22"/>騁六塵。<note n="0003041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不〕&M062403;－【原】，不＝無【敦】</note><app n="0003041"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>暫停息。宜<note n="0003042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝及【敦】</note><app n="0003042"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">及</rdg></app>信心預自剋念。便
<lb n="0003c23"/>積習成<note n="0003043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">性＝往&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0003043"><lem>性</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">往</rdg></app>。善根堅固也。如佛告頻婆娑羅
<lb n="0003c24"/>王。人積善行。死無惡念。如樹西傾。必倒隨
<lb n="0003c25"/><note n="0003044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曲＋（也）【敦】</note><app n="0003044"><lem>曲</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">曲也</rdg></app>。若<app type="＊" source="0003005"><lem>便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【敦】">使</rdg></app>刀風一至。百苦湊身。<note n="0003045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若習前＝習【敦】</note><app n="0003045"><lem>若習前</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">習</rdg></app>不
<lb n="0003c26"/>在。懷念何可辨。又宜同志五三共結言要。垂
<lb n="0003c27"/>命終時。迭相開曉。為稱阿彌陀佛名號願生
<lb n="0003c28"/>安樂。聲聲相次。使成十念也。譬如蠟印印泥。
<lb n="0003c29"/>印壞文成。此命斷時。即是生安<note n="0003046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樂＋（國）【敦】</note><app n="0003046"><lem>樂</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">樂國</rdg></app>時。一入
<pb ed="T" id="T47.1957.0004a" n="0004a"/>
<lb n="0004a01"/>正定聚。更何所憂<note n="0004001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【敦】</note><app n="0004001"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0004a02"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0004002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">略論安樂淨土義畢＝讚阿彌陀佛并論上卷【敦】</note><app n="0004002"><lem>略論安樂淨土義<note place="inline">畢</note></lem><rdg wit="【敦】" resp="Taisho">讚阿彌陀佛并論上卷</rdg></app><note n="0004003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下燉煌本奧書曰景雲二年三月十九日弟子張萬及寫</note></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>